rner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 AFC \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t v\u1edbi CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a do \u0111\u1ec3 ra sai ph\u1ea1m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i AFC Cup 2018.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CLB FLC Thanh Hoa nhan an phat cua LDBD chau A  hinh anh\" title=\"CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/thanh-hoa-bat-ngo-linh-an-phat-cua-ldbd-chau-a.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t 6000 USD c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1eeb AFC do \u0111\u1ec3 ra sai ph\u1ea1m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i AFC Cup 2018.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t do vi ph\u1ea1m hai l\u1ed7i trong c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Global Cebu tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh h\u00f4m 10/2.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">AFC n\u00eau r\u00f5 \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1 qu\u00e2n V-League 2018 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c an ninh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u00f3 g\u1ea7n 10 C\u0110V tr\u00e0n xu\u1ed1ng khu v\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng pitch, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ea7m sau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng an ninh s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng \u0111eo th\u1ebb ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean hay nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u1edbi khu v\u1ef1c ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i. S\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a AFC \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y ghi l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 b\u00e1o l\u00ean ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 2 l\u1ed7i tr\u00ean, AFC \u0111\u00e3 ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t 6.000 USD (h\u01a1n 120 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng) v\u1edbi FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc l\u1edbn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi ra s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Highlight Thanh H\u00f3a vs SLNA (V\u00f2ng 4 V-League)</em></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/1/Highlight-Thanh-Hoa-vs-SLNA-vong-4-vleague.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/chum-anh-co-dong-vien-doi-ao-36-va-37-trong-tran-thanh-hoa-vs-slna-291-183330.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/1/chum-anh-co-dong-vien-doi-ao-36-va-37-trong-tran-thanh-hoa-vs-slna.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/chum-anh-co-dong-vien-doi-ao-36-va-37-trong-tran-thanh-hoa-vs-slna-291-183330.html\">Ch\u00f9m \u1ea3nh: C\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed5i \u00e1o 36 v\u00e0 37 trong tr\u1eadn derby B\u1eafc Trung B\u1ed9</span><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, s\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec7t th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean t\u1ea1o n\u00ean d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t cho tr\u1eadn derby B\u1eafc Trung B\u1ed9 gi\u1eefa FLC Thanh H\u00f3a vs...</div>\r\n</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"771","checkdouble":"183450"},{"date":"16:56 03/04","title":"Trong l\u00fac ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Tu\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/trong-luc-chan-thuong-tuan-anh-doi-kieu-dau-cuc-chat.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-