th: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT nu Viet Nam dat chan toi Jordan chuan bi cho giac mo World Cup hinh anh\" title=\"\u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n t\u1edbi Jordan chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/DT-nu-Viet-Nam-dat-chan-toi-Jordan-chuan-bi-cho-giac-mo-World-Cup-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Jordan \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho\u00a0VCK Asian Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ebfn bay th\u1eb3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung k\u00e9o d\u00e0i g\u1ea7n 4 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3, h\u1ea1 c\u00e1nh xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n bay qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf Amman l\u00fac 2h10 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 3/4 (gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng).\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam nhanh ch\u00f3ng l\u1ea5y h\u00e0nh l\u00fd v\u00e0 di chuy\u1ec3n v\u1ec1 kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n. \u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ed9i Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u00e2n trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Amman l\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n Holliday Inn, n\u1eb1m ngay gi\u1eefa trung t\u00e2m th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Amman c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Jordan c\u1ed5 k\u00ednh.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn bay d\u00e0i n\u00ean HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e3 cho ph\u00e9p c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ngh\u1ec9 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp s\u00e1ng nay v\u00e0 s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay 3/4 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp l\u00e0m quen s\u00e2n v\u00e0 th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft t\u1ea1i Amman.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi n\u1eef Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o l\u00fac 20h45 ng\u00e0y 6/4 t\u1edbi (gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam). Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u00dac l\u00fac 0h00 ng\u00e0y 10/4 v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00fac 20h45 ng\u00e0y 12/4.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"753","checkdouble":"183444"}]}